Uche Devon Eke (amuru 12 Ọgọst 1997) bu onye onye mgbatị ahụ ndi Naijiria-Amerika
Ọ meriri ọla edo na 2019 All-Africa Games na Morocco
Ọ ghọrọ onye egwuregwu mbụ na-anọchi anya Nigeria na mgbatị ahụ n'egwuregwu Olympik ka o sonyere na mmemme mgbatị ahụ nke Summer Olympics Tokyo 2020,   ebe ọ gbachara 36th n'ozuzu ya
Eke nwetara nzere masta na sayensị ozi na Mahadum Michigan
